                { id: 17, topic: "Castor Bean", front: "What is the toxic principle and its mechanism?", back: "Ricin (Phytotoxin). It has two chains: one binds cells, the other inhibits protein synthesis." },
                { id: 18, topic: "Castor Bean", front: "How toxic are the seeds?", back: "One chewed seed can be fatal. Un-chewed seeds may pass harmlessly." },
